Maggie McOmie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maggie_McOmie 0 Maggie McOmie is an American stage and film actress, best known for co-starring with Robert Duvall in George Lucas' 1971 film THX 1138. Though the film received mixed reviews at the time, it has since developed a cult following.
